name: Italy NFT
description: Unique NFT country Italy. The base is made of crystal, which stands on the famous Leaning Tower of Pisa, which is made of gold. The stand is made of pure glass. On a stand made of blue crystal, a pond from Venice is made on which a Gondola with a gondolier floats with the help of a mechanism. Along the edges, 2 Ferraris of the 308 series also drive with the help of the mechanism. Inside the stand, you can see all the mechanical gears. Behind the stand is an oven where pizza is supposedly cooked.
